______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

COMPUTE

TYPES OF COMPUTE OPTIONS

1.VM (Elastic Compute Cloud-EC2)
2.Containers
3.Servers 

EC2:

*compatible with Linux, Windows, MacOS
*compute capacity expressed in vCPUs (virtual CPUs), memory , network capacity and connected storage.
*disposable resources (setup and remove easily)
*Vertical scaling --> larger or smaller Instance
 Horizontal scaling --> number of instances

AWS Lambda:

*Best for short running stateless code.
